text: Rafał Dobrowolski (born 27 December 1983) is an archer from Poland. Dobrowolski competed at the 2008 Summer Olympics and the 2012 Summer Olympics.Rafał DobrowolskiRafal DOBROWOLSKI == References == Category:1983 births Category:Living people Category:Polish archers Category:Olympians for Poland
